parameters: ストーリー　砦潜入　敗北
アクター HK_重戦士01-1
アクター HK_重戦士01-1
\n< Adventurer >Ugh, this area is especially shitty.

\n< Adventurer >Both the right and left sides are filled with
black slimes.
\n< Adventurer >That means we're getting closer to the center.

\n< Adventurer >Found it. It's a landmark. The previous party
turned back here.
\n< Adventurer >If there's a target, it's ahead.
\n< Adventurer >Let's go with all our might.
\n< Adventurer >Oh.
\n< Adventurer >.......
\n< Adventurer >.......
\n< Adventurer >Ugh... Oh...
\n< Adventurer >Huge... What the hell is this...
\n< Adventurer >Hey, over there. Look.
\n< Adventurer >Ugh...

\n< Adventurer >Finally, we meet... Ah, as rumored, such a
breathtaking beauty that sends shivers down my
spine...
\n< Adventurer >Oh, the pitiful princess Serena de Gracia...
$gameScreen.showPicture(13,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-素体-ストレート",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(18,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-装飾-ピアス",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(23,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-装飾-入れ墨",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(27,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-表情-眉05",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-表情-目05",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
\n< Serena >.......
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-表情-目02",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
\n< Serena >.......

\n< Adventurer >Even a high-ranking princess like you has ended up
like this... How many years have you been giving
birth to failures in this underground place...

\n< Adventurer >Just to confirm, it's okay if we don't capture
them alive, right?
\n< Adventurer >Ah... The request is for extermination.
$gameScreen.showPicture(13,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-素体-ストレート",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(18,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-装飾-ピアス",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(23,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-装飾-入れ墨",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(27,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-表情-眉05",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-表情-目01",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)

\n< Adventurer >It used to be a rescue mission before. But now,
even the client has finally given up...
\n< Adventurer >Hey, I just made eye contact with her.
\n< Adventurer >It's just a reflex. I'm not looking at anything.

\n< Adventurer >...I've strangled many of your fellow colleagues
before. Don't even think for a second that I'll
help you.
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-表情-目02",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
\n< Adventurer >I understand. I was just confirming.
\n< Adventurer >Alright. I'm ready. Anytime is fine.

\n< Adventurer >That person is still observing. Let's give them
the advantage and wait for their move.

\n< Adventurer >Let's go with number 3. If we're lucky, we can cut
off their heads right from the start.

\n< Adventurer >Let's finish this soon. Let's give the poor
princess a taste of hell.

\n< Adventurer >Ah... Since Gracia is willing to pay a lot of
money!!
